These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, skateboard, roller, motorbike
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, milk, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, snowboarding, badminton
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, mystery, musical, action
1. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | boat  | motorbike  | skateboard | roller |
| Beverage           | fanta | iced-tea | coffee  | milk  |
| Sport   | badminton       | snowboarding      | tennis | cycling      |
| Movie-Genre           | drama          | mystery     | musical    | action     |

