.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
House: farmhouse, modern, townhouse, victorian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, daisy, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, may, june
4 different pets are kept: rat, fish, ferret, frog
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the modern house##1
8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
9. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House      | townhouse     | farmhouse       | modern | victorian        |
| Flower          | bellflower     | aconite       | daisy   | marigold   |
| Birthday   | may      | january       | june     | september    |
| Pet         | ferret | frog | rat | fish |

