.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indian, brazilian, british
City: paris, london, venice, marseilles
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, march, may
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, car, motorbike
 1. the british is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the brazilian is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the turkish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the brazilian is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Nationality      | indian | turkish       | british        | brazilian        |
| City           | london   | venice | paris   | marseilles |
| Birthday   | june     | october    | may | march        |
| Transport           | car         | scooter  | motorbike       | tram         |

