.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, documentary, fantasy, horror
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, august, december
House: farmhouse, cottage, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, lily, amaryllis
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
9. the person who growslily is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary   | mystery  | horror | fantasy |
| Birthday   | august | december       | may       | april     |
| House   | cape-cod       | ranch-style    | cottage     | farmhouse  |
| Flower           | tulip     | lily | amaryllis     | begonia         |

