.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, taxi, jet-ski, car
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, bridge, go
House: colonial, victorian, townhouse, modern
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, traveling, drawing, writing
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the townhouse house##1
7. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person playing chess##1
9. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Transport           | tram  | jet-ski    | taxi | car |
| Game   | bridge      | chess    | monopoly         | go    |
| House   | victorian   | colonial     | townhouse          | modern      |
| Hobby         | traveling | camping | writing      | drawing      |

