.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, billiard, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, italian, japanese, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, tiparillo, chaman, alhambra
 1. the person playing billiard is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the polish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the pakistani##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the japanese is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the japanese is on the far left##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | monopoly  | poker | billiard     | canasta |
| Nationality           | japanese  | pakistani      | polish | italian    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice  | hot-chocolate    | milk  |
| Cigar           | chaman   | alhambra       | swisher       | tiparillo      |

