.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bluemaster, siglo, fonseca
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, salsa, disco, blues
There 4 different types of food: papaya, zucchini, blueberry, cucumber
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, egyptian, pakistani
 1. the person eating papaya is the fan of salsa##1
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 7. the person eating papaya is the egyptian##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the american is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar    | montecristo | bluemaster     | siglo    | fonseca |
| Music-Genre       | pop | disco    | blues | salsa |
| Food         | zucchini   | blueberry  | cucumber        | papaya    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | argentine | american    | egyptian |

