7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the chaman-smoker is the fan of jazz##1
9. the havana-smoker is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | pop      | jazz         | punk        | funk      |
