.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, bridge, domino
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, carrot, cauliflower, raspberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, romance, comedy
City: berlin, nizza, marseilles, hamburg
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
4. the person playing bridge is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
8. the person eating carrot is the person playing domino##1
9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Game      | backgammon     | domino           | monopoly    | bridge    |
| Food         | cauliflower  | carrot | blueberry  | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | adventure     | family | comedy   |
| City         | hamburg | berlin     | nizza | marseilles     |

